{"tid":1115143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英國華女會計師跟蹤教授一年 被斥︰骯髒的變態","createTime":"2019-04-19T03:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T03:37:03.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"29c7c5789da2cadf14cdbaaa365d0b1a8287b00c","tid":1115143,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%8F%AF%E5%A5%B3%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E5%B8%AB%E8%B7%9F%E8%B9%A4%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E8%A2%AB%E6%96%A5%EF%B8%B0%E9%AA%AF%E9%AB%92%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%8A%E6%85%8B-005720650.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25B7%259F%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2596%25A5%25EF%25B8%25B0%25E9%25AA%25AF%25E9%25AB%2592%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2585%258B-005720650.html&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=a79cd012\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%8F%AF%E5%A5%B3%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E5%B8%AB%E8%B7%9F%E8%B9%A4%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E8%A2%AB%E6%96%A5%EF%B8%B0%E9%AA%AF%E9%AB%92%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%8A%E6%85%8B-005720650.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2t841SRaCxzjMKcFCqguSQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/421d767f3c3742b3d11432087949eed0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2t841SRaCxzjMKcFCqguSQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F421d767f3c3742b3d11432087949eed0&h=5f5f7317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n埃德曼（左）與李招燕（右）。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦40歲華裔女會計師李招燕（音譯，Zhaoyan Li），涉嫌跟蹤騷擾倫敦商業學院金融系教授埃德曼（Alex Edmans）長達一年半，令埃德曼生活大受影響。案件周三（17日）在法院提堂，李女否認控罪，更揚言被判刑可能會自殺。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒報道，李女在2017年某次基督教宣傳活動上聽到埃德曼的演說後，便對他產生極大興趣。<span style=\"color: red;\">李女先是到埃德曼經常出現的教堂和健身中心，其後又以短訊、電話及電郵「轟炸」他，甚至在他與朋友的合照中「偷偷冒出」。</span>埃德曼雖然在去年1月曾報警，警方亦警告李女，惟她未有放棄，更在同年2月14日致電埃德曼說：「情人節快樂。」<br />\n<br />\n埃德曼向法官形容，這場「漫長的折磨」令他感到恐懼，他被迫退出教會團契、不敢接聽辦公室電話，甚至會害怕檢查電郵。他曾離開英國飛到西班牙渡假，惟李女竟仍一直跟蹤他。最終，他擔心得要在辦公室內安裝緊急報警器。<br />\n<br />\n檢察官則透露，李女遇見埃德曼後，便不斷騷擾他；埃德曼曾多次明示暗示李女，<span style=\"color: red;\">試過踩住她雙腳警告不要在公眾場合喧嘩，卻被對方誤會為「性暗示」，甚至曾當面直斥：「別站在那裏，你這個骯髒的變態。」李女反而要求埃德曼道歉。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣比人纏法有咩辦法甩身"},{"pid":"01f7e4e7b67ba4c924a7b8f2827f40a1461f5f99","tid":1115143,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當</span>"},{"pid":"9694c5c38ba911e11f20216e61a0e580b58013b9","tid":1115143,"uid":30710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"睇個樣都覺得佢痴痴地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b5d435d952416a71baa3937d1fd8c4b9103cd1","tid":1115143,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:34:18.000Z","msg":"支那女人用美人計不成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208c6245e8257095dca1ea2453c519cfc927eeb9","tid":1115143,"uid":234317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:36:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"095e0f987c09114bb7b564dc2219816c5ad1600d","tid":1115143,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"點踩住她雙腳"}]}